data.text:
Dozois, Gardner. STRANGERS. New York: Published by Berkley Publishing Corporation Distributed by G. P. Putnam's Sons, [1978]. Octavo, cloth. First edition. "An intricate and melancholy tale of love and biological mystery on a distant world." - Robert Silverberg. The author's first novel. 1978 Nebula nominee. Anatomy of Wonder (2004) II-356. A review copy with review slip, publisher's promotional sheet and publicity photograph of Dozois laid in. A fine copy in fine dust jacket. (#157632).

Price: $75.00
